> You live you learn.
I have a 50 pin cable cable coming out the back to the Jaz drive, then a 50
pin cable going to an external hard drive, then a 50-to-25 pin cable going
to the Zip drive.
> JOOI, did your drives allow you to eject them whilst mounted?
> Do you still have them to test this
Yes, I still have them.  I use them frequently.  I cannot eject them while
mounted.  However, if I do try to eject them when mounted, they will
automatically eject when unmounted.
